title: THE GEORGE BURNS SHOW -- La Vie En Rose
description:
This was actually the ninth and final TV season of 
"The George Burns and Gracie Allen Show" ( Season 17 if we include the
identical radio series before it)....minus Gracie, 
who retired from show business in 1958. The rest of the established cast 
was still there.  She's still mentioned by George, who is seen 
working from his office rather than being at home.

Gracie died in 1964, which ironically was the same year that George returned 
to weekly television in "Wendy and Me" co-starring Connie Stevens.
